By: @lumadeline

Location: Dolomitenhütte, Tirol, Austria 🇦🇹

#roomwithaview #view #viewfrommywindow #views #vacation #viewsfordays #austria #mountain #mountains

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Millionaire Surroundings 🎩 on August 30, 2021 tagging @jacobandco, and @millionaire.surroundings. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
@jacobandco Astronomia Art Dragon Mother Of Pearl 😍

What sets this watch apart from others is its sense of occasion, created by the stunning sapphire Crystal and precious metal case.

Within the Sapphire, Crystal dome lurks the mystical dragon handcrafted by the artisans at Jacob & Co from 18k gold. One other feature unique to this iteration of the ‘dragon’ series is the base dial made entirely of mother-of-Pearl.

Thanks again to @jacobandco for allowing us to showcase this watch with breathtaking designs.

#millionairesurroundings #jacobandco

#watch #watchesofinstagram #watches #watchcollector #watchaddict #artisan #limitededition #artisanmade

node.text:
@jacobandco Opera Godfather Musical Watch 🔥

Created in official partnership with Paramount Pictures, the producer and distributor company of The Godfather, the Opera Godfather utilises its bespoke complication of two rotating drums with a total of 36 teeth turning against two combs to play a melody of 120 notes of The Godfather theme music.

If you look closely, you can notice the 18k gold piano keys moving, making contact with the pins of the cylinder, which produces the iconic soundtrack.

Jacob & Co is breaking traditional watchmaking rules with this stunning piece, wouldn’t you agree?

By: @jacobandco | #millionairesurroundings #jacobandco

#watch #watches #watchesofinstagram #watchcollector #godfather #limitededition #thegodfather #gangster

node.text:
@jacobandco Astronomia Everest Black Gold 🏔

Jacob & Co using their famous Astronomia line to pay homage to the Swedish explorer Johan Ernst Nilsson, who took the Everest Black Gold with him on an expedition to the Himalayas.

The words of Nilson “You would think that such a complicated watch would be delicate and fragile, but it isn't, and it performed perfectly in all conditions. I used it climbing up ice walls, with my ice axe, banging it against rock and ice, and it held up extremely well."

By: @jacobandco

#millionairesurroundings #jacobandco #everest #watch #watches #watchoftheday #watchesofinstagram #watchcollector #watchfam #watchaddict
